        <h3>EHDSHumanName → HumanName</h3>
        <p class="lead">
      This page describes the element-by-element mapping from the
            <a href="https://www.xt-ehr.eu/fhir/models/StructureDefinition/EHDSHumanName">
                <strong>EHDSHumanName</strong>
            </a>
      logical model to the HL7 FHIR
            <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/datatypes.html#HumanName">
                <strong>HumanName</strong>
            </a>
      datatype, as used in this Implementation Guide.
        </p>
        <div class="legend">
            <strong>Relationship legend</strong>
            <dl>
                <dt>equal</dt>
                <dd>Semantically equivalent: the meaning of the EHDS element matches the FHIR element directly.</dd>
                <dt>narrower</dt>
                <dd>The FHIR element is more specific / more constrained than the EHDS element.</dd>
                <dt>relatedto</dt>
                <dd>The EHDS element maps to the target concept but not 1:1 (e.g. requires context or transformation).</dd>
                <dt>unmatched</dt>
                <dd>No corresponding element in this FHIR profile/datatype.</dd>
            </dl>
        </div>
